--- a/responder_prog.R
+++ b/responder_prog.R
@@ -1,5 +1,5 @@
-Bug 1: Responder definition uses AVAL > BASE (improvement in any direction) instead of specified threshold (e.g., >=4 point improvement)
+Fix 1: Responder uses specified improvement threshold
@@ -1,5 +1,5 @@
