Summary of fixes:
1. Responder uses specified improvement threshold (responder_definition)
2. CMH test uses mantelhaen.test() for stratified analysis (cmh_test)
3. Response rates use group-specific denominators (rate_denominator)
4. Missing values excluded from responder analysis (missing_handling)
